       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COI87102.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COI87102.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Manutençăo de Contas                                       *
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI87102         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD3606 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD5403 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV8710.
       COPY COCV8711.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY COCK0001.
       COPY COCK0002.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-COVT3606 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT3606'.
           05 CON-COVT5403 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT5403'.
           05 CON-PR       PIC X(02) VALUE 'PR'.
           05 CON-001      PIC 9(03) VALUE 001.
           05 CON-S        PIC X(01) VALUE 'S'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARIAVEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-CSIGLA                    PIC X(03) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-PROJECTO                  PIC X(08).
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-PROJECTO.
              10 WS-PROJECTO-SIGLA         PIC X(03) VALUE SPACES.
              10 WS-PROJECTO-NUM           PIC 9(05) VALUE ZEROS.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME            PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COI87102'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI87102         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0004.

            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.

           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO COCV8710-MSG.
           MOVE COCV8710-ASE       TO COCV8711-ASE.

       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV8710-ADE       TO COCV8711-ADE.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2050-VALIDACAO
                 THRU 2050-VALIDACAO-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2100-OBTEM-DADOS
                 THRU 2199-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * 2050-VALIDACAO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2050-VALIDACAO.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2050-VALIDACAO    ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *--- SE CRIACAO ---*
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND VIAL0001-CRIACAO
           AND COCV8710-CLIENTE EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV8711-CLIENTE-S
               MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV8711-CLIENTE-MSG
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV8711-CLIENTE-CAPLIC
           END-IF.
      *
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND VIAL0001-CRIACAO
           AND COCV8710-NIDPROJECTO EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV8711-NIDPROJECTO-S
               MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT
                 TO COCV8711-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                 TO COCV8711-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

      *--- SE NĂO FOR CRIACAO ---*
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
           AND NOT VIAL0001-CRIACAO
           AND COCV8710-NIDPROJECTO EQUAL SPACES
               MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
               MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV8711-NIDPROJECTO-S
               MOVE COCK0001-CAMPO-OBRIGAT TO COCV8711-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
               MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC TO COCV8711-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
           END-IF.

      *--- SEJA OU NĂO CRIAÇĂO ---*
           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
               PERFORM 2055-VER-CLIENTE
                  THRU 2055-VER-CLIENTE-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF  VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
               MOVE COCV8710-NIDPROJECTO TO WS-PROJECTO
               IF WS-PROJECTO-SIGLA NOT EQUAL WS-CSIGLA
                  MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                  MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV8711-NIDPROJECTO-S
                  MOVE COCK0001-CONTA-FMT-INV
                    TO COCV8711-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
                  MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                    TO COCV8711-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
               END-IF

               IF WS-PROJECTO-NUM NOT NUMERIC
                  MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                  MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV8711-NIDPROJECTO-S
                  MOVE COCK0001-CONTA-FMT-INV
                    TO COCV8711-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
                  MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                    TO COCV8711-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
               END-IF

           END-IF.

       2050-VALIDACAO-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * 2055-VER-CLIENTE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2055-VER-CLIENTE.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2055-VER-CLIENTE  ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *    MOVE COCV8710-CLIENTE TO COCD5403-CEMPRESA.
           MOVE COCV8710-CLIENTE TO COCD5403-CSIGLA.

           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT CEMPRESA,
                        GMARCA,
                        IVIA,
                        CPAIS,
                        CSIGLA,
                        CMOEDA
                 INTO  :COCD5403-CEMPRESA,
                       :COCD5403-GMARCA,
                       :COCD5403-IVIA,
                       :COCD5403-CPAIS,
                       :COCD5403-CSIGLA,
                       :COCD5403-CMOEDA
                 FROM COVT5403_EMPRESAS
      *          WHERE CEMPRESA = :COCD5403-CEMPRESA
                 WHERE CSIGLA   = :COCD5403-CSIGLA
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-COVT5403 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
             IF DB2-OK
               CONTINUE
             ELSE
               IF DB2-NOTFND
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV8711-CLIENTE-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-CLIENTE-N-EXISTS TO
                                COCV8711-CLIENTE-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC TO COCV8711-CLIENTE-CAPLIC
               END-IF
             END-IF
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCD5403-CSIGLA            TO WS-CSIGLA.
           MOVE COCD5403-CPAIS             TO COCV8711-PAIS.
           MOVE COCD5403-CMOEDA            TO COCV8711-CMOEDA.
           MOVE COCD5403-CPAIS             TO COCV8710-PAIS.
           MOVE COCD5403-CMOEDA            TO COCV8710-CMOEDA.

       2055-VER-CLIENTE-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-OBTEM-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-OBTEM-DADOS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-OBTEM-DADOS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'COCV8710-NIDPROJECTO   ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  COCV8710-NIDPROJECTO     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              MOVE 'COCV8710-CLIENTE       ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE  COCV8710-CLIENTE         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

      *
      *    IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
      *       IF  VIAL0001-CRIACAO
      *       AND COCV8710-NIDPROJECTO = SPACES
      *           PERFORM 2200-OBTEM-DADOS-CRIA
      *              THRU 2200-OBTEM-DADOS-CRIA-EXIT
      *       END-IF
      *    END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2300-OBTEM-DADOS
                 THRU 2300-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2199-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * 2200-OBTEM-DADOS-CRIA (COM PROJECTO A ESPAÇOS)
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *2200-OBTEM-DADOS-CRIA.
      *
      *    IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
      *       MOVE '2200-OBTEM-DADOS-CRIA'   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
      *       PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
      *          THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
      *    END-IF.
      *
      *    MOVE WS-CSIGLA             TO COCD3606-CLIENTE.
      *
      *    EXEC SQL
      *         SELECT  IFNULL (MAX(NIDPROJECTO), " ")
      *           INTO :COCD3606-NIDPROJECTO
      *           FROM  COVT3606_PROJECTS
      *          WHERE  CLIENTE = :COCD3606-CLIENTE
      *    END-EXEC.
      *
      *    MOVE CON-COVT3606 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
      *    PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
      *       THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
      *    SET VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS TO TRUE.
      *
      *    MOVE WS-CSIGLA                  TO WS-PROJECTO-SIGLA.
      *    MOVE CON-PR                     TO WS-PROJECTO-PR.
      *    MOVE CON-001                    TO WS-PROJECTO-NUM.
      *
      *    IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
      *       IF COCD3606-NIDPROJECTO NOT EQUAL SPACES
      *          MOVE COCD3606-NIDPROJECTO TO WS-PROJECTO
      *          ADD 1                     TO WS-PROJECTO-NUM
      *       END-IF
      *    END-IF.
      *
      *    MOVE WS-PROJECTO                TO COCD3606-NIDPROJECTO.
      *    MOVE COCD3606-NIDPROJECTO       TO COCV8711-NIDPROJECTO.
      *    MOVE COCD3606-NIDPROJECTO       TO COCV8710-NIDPROJECTO.
      *
      *2200-OBTEM-DADOS-CRIA-EXIT.
      *    EXIT.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2300-OBTEM-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2300-OBTEM-DADOS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2300-OBTEM-DADOS     '   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV8710-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCD3606-NIDPROJECTO.

           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT
                       NIDPROJECTO
                     , CPROJECT
                     , GDESCPROJECT
                     , DBEGINDATE
                     , DENDDATE
                     , NPERCENTALERT
                     , DALERTDATE
                     , CMOEDA
                     , BACTIVE
                     , NBUDGET
                     , PAIS
                     , CLIENTE
                     , LINHANEG
                     , RESPONS
                     , IPROJI
                     , IPROJE
                     , IACHORAS
                     , IADESPESAS
                     , TPPFAT
                     , CUSERID
                     , HTIMEST
                     , TIPONEG
                     , DADJUDATE
                     , GJUSTORC
                     , COPORTUNITY
                     , DALTSTAT
                     , CEMPRESA
                     , ICTACUST
                     , CREVPG
                 INTO
                       :COCD3606-NIDPROJECTO
                     , :COCD3606-CPROJECT
                     , :COCD3606-GDESCPROJECT
                     , :COCD3606-DBEGINDATE
                     , :COCD3606-DENDDATE
                     , :COCD3606-NPERCENTALERT
                     , :COCD3606-DALERTDATE
                     , :COCD3606-CMOEDA
                     , :COCD3606-BACTIVE
                     , :COCD3606-NBUDGET
                     , :COCD3606-PAIS
                     , :COCD3606-CLIENTE
                     , :COCD3606-LINHANEG
                     , :COCD3606-RESPONS
                     , :COCD3606-IPROJI
                     , :COCD3606-IPROJE
                     , :COCD3606-IACHORAS
                     , :COCD3606-IADESPESAS
                     , :COCD3606-TPPFAT
                     , :COCD3606-CUSERID
                     , :COCD3606-HTIMEST
                     , :COCD3606-TIPONEG
                     , :COCD3606-DADJUDATE
                     , :COCD3606-GJUSTORC
                     , :COCD3606-COPORTUNITY
                     , :COCD3606-DALTSTAT
                     , :COCD3606-CEMPRESA
                     , :COCD3606-ICTACUST
                     , :COCD3606-CREVPG
                  FROM  COVT3606_PROJECTS
                 WHERE  NIDPROJECTO = :COCD3606-NIDPROJECTO
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-COVT3606 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 IF VIAL0001-CRIACAO
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO COCV8711-NIDPROJECTO-S
                    MOVE COCK0001-NIDPROJECTO-EXISTS
                      TO COCV8711-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
                    MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                      TO COCV8711-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
                 ELSE
      *            IF COCD3606-ICTACUST EQUAL COCK0002-SIM
                   IF COCD3606-ICTACUST EQUAL COCK0002-NAO
                     MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                       TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                     MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                       TO COCV8711-NIDPROJECTO-S
                     MOVE COCK0001-CTACUST-NAO-CST
                       TO COCV8711-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
                     MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                       TO COCV8711-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
                   ELSE
                     MOVE COCD3606-NIDPROJECTO
                       TO COCV8711-NIDPROJECTO
                     MOVE COCD3606-CPROJECT
                       TO COCV8711-CPROJECT
                     MOVE COCD3606-GDESCPROJECT
                       TO COCV8711-GDESCPROJECT
                     MOVE COCD3606-DADJUDATE
                       TO COCV8711-DADJUDATE
                     MOVE COCD3606-DBEGINDATE
                       TO COCV8711-DBEGINDATE
                     MOVE COCD3606-DENDDATE
                       TO COCV8711-DENDDATE
                     MOVE COCD3606-NPERCENTALERT
                       TO COCV8711-NPERCENTALERT
                     MOVE COCD3606-DALERTDATE
                       TO COCV8711-DALERTDATE
                     MOVE COCD3606-BACTIVE
                       TO COCV8711-BACTIVE
                     MOVE COCD3606-BACTIVE
                       TO COCV8711-BACTIVE-ANT
                     MOVE COCD3606-NBUDGET
                       TO COCV8711-NBUDGET
                     MOVE COCD3606-CMOEDA
                       TO COCV8711-CMOEDA
                     MOVE COCD3606-PAIS
                       TO COCV8711-PAIS
      *              MOVE COCD3606-CLIENTE
      *                TO COCV8711-CLIENTE
                     MOVE COCD3606-LINHANEG
                       TO COCV8711-LINHANEG
                     MOVE COCD3606-TIPONEG
                       TO COCV8711-TIPONEG
                     MOVE COCD3606-RESPONS
                       TO COCV8711-RESPONS
                     MOVE COCD3606-TPPFAT
                       TO COCV8711-TPPFAT
                     MOVE COCD3606-DALTSTAT
                       TO COCV8711-DALTSTAT
                     MOVE COCD3606-CREVPG
                       TO COCV8711-CREVPG
                   END-IF
                 END-IF
              ELSE
                 IF NOT VIAL0001-CRIACAO
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO COCV8711-NIDPROJECTO-S
                    MOVE COCK0001-NIDPROJECTO-N-EXISTS
                      TO COCV8711-NIDPROJECTO-MSG
                    MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                      TO COCV8711-NIDPROJECTO-CAPLIC
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2300-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'COCV8711-PAIS        ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(2)
              MOVE  COCV8711-PAIS          TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(2)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV8711-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE COCV8711-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE COCV8711-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *==============================================================
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0016.
